Follow [docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](docs/ARCHITECTURE.md) strictly.

Architecture constraints:
- Routes and Server Actions stay thin: validate, call services, revalidate, return UI state.
- Non-trivial Prisma access belongs in `src/services/*` using the shared client from `src/lib/db.ts`.
- Zod schemas live in `src/lib/validations/*`.

When fixing bugs:
- Prefer writing or updating tests first.
- Do not modify files outside the mentioned module.
- If changes are required outside the module, explain first before editing.

Never refactor unrelated modules without explicit instruction.
